::Striker::

Striker jumps up as he hears Spears over his comm-link, taking off at a run 
toward the bridge. It sounded like something had collapsed on her. He enters 
the bridge, raising an eyebrow when he sees Spears, black with ash. He 
chucles.

"New look?"
